<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
  	<title>成语检索</title>
  	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,
  	initial-scale=1.0" charset="utf-8">
  	<script src="/public/jquery-1.8.0.js"></script>
  	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/bootstrap.css" />
  	<script src="/public/bootstrap.js"></script>
  	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/app.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
  	<div class="navbar navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="navbar-header">
          <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".navbar-collapse">
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          </button>
          <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">成语检索</a>
        </div>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse">
          <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
          </ul>
        </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
    	<div id="dashboard">
    		<div class="row">
    			<h3>成语检索</h3>

    			<p>
    			本站收集了一些常用的成语（20000个以上）并创建了一个小的应用，帮助你找到包含特殊字符的成语。	
    			</p>
    			<hr />
    		</div>

    		<div class="row">
    			<p>输入成语包含的汉字，需要时使用 _ （看下面的使用介绍）</p>

    			<form method="post" action="search">
    				<% if(pattern) { %>
                      <input type="text"
                             class="col-md-12" 
                             name="pattern"
                             placeholder="请在此处输入"
                             value="<%= pattern%>" 
                             />    
    				<% } else { %>
                      <input type="text"
                             class="col-md-12" 
                             name="pattern"
                             placeholder="请在此处输入"
                             />   
    				<% } %>
    			</form>
    		</div>
    		<hr />